dct_title_s: Watershed Assessment 1:24,000 Hydrography: Russian River Basin, California, 1998
dct_description_sm: This line shapefile represents the hydrography of the Russian River basin in California. This layer is a portion of the original Watershed Assessment 1:24,000 Hydrography layer created by the California Department of Forestry and Fire Protection.
This shapefile provides seamless enhanced hydrography data of the Russian River Watershed by river basin, modified for hydrologic modeling.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
